flowchart TD
    Input[User Input] --> Redactor[Privacy Redactor]
    Redactor -->|Safe for Cloud| Cloud[Cloud Model via Ollama]
    Redactor -->|Contains PII/Sensitive| Local[Local Model Only]
    Cloud --> Agent[ARIA Agent]
    Local --> Agent
    Agent --> ToolCall{Tool Call?}
    ToolCall -->|No| Response[Text Response]
    ToolCall -->|Yes| Allowlist{In TOOL_ALLOWLIST?}
    Allowlist -->|No| Reject[Rejected]
    Allowlist -->|Yes| RiskCheck{Risk Tier?}
    RiskCheck -->|Low/Medium| Execute[Execute Tool]
    RiskCheck -->|High| Approval[Request User Approval]
    Approval -->|Approved| Execute
    Approval -->|Denied| Cancelled[Action Cancelled]
    Execute --> Sandbox["RLIMIT Sandbox"]
